          "payload": "AAEAAAD/////AQAAAAAAAAAEAQAAAA9TeXN0ZW0uSW50MzJbXQEAAAAITG93Qm91bmQIAAAAAAAAAA==",
          "description": ".NET BinaryFormatter Int32 array probe (base64) — safe object that triggers deserialization; error mentioning BinaryFormatter or SerializationException confirms .NET deserialization is active",
          "matchers": [
